{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "Payment API - Complete Workflow",
    "description": "Complete test suite for Payment Pillar\n\nBased on: specs/payment/payment.pillar.v2.yml\n\nCovers:\n- Payment method management\n- Payment intent lifecycle (create \u2192 confirm \u2192 succeed/fail/cancel)\n- Receipt issuance and voiding (admin)\n- Webhook ingestion\n\nWorkflow order:\n1. Create a payment method\n2. Create a payment intent (optionally referencing the method)\n3. Confirm the intent with a provider\n4. Mark succeeded or failed (admin)\n5. Issue a receipt (admin)\n6. Void the receipt if needed (admin)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
